ciscoIfExtensionCapability.name: ciscoIfExtensionCapability

revisions.description: Added ciscoIfExtensionTableIntfGroup3SupR02 and VARIATIONs for cieIfTransceiverFrequencyConfig, cieIfFillPatternConfig, cieIfIgnoreBitErrorsConfig and cieIfIgnoreInterruptThresholdConfig in capability statement ciscoIfExtCapNxOSV06R0201PMDS9000 and ciscoIfExtCapNxOSV06R0202PN7K.
Added agent capability statement ciscoIfExtCapNxOSV06R0201PMDS9000 and ciscoIfExtCapNxOSV06R0202PN7K.
Added ciscoIfExtCapc4710aceVA1R700 agent capabilities for ACE 4710 Application Control Engine Appliance.
Added ciscoIfExtCapV12R0229SM1 and ciscoIfExtCapV12R0412MR1 capability statements.
Added capability statement ciscoIfExtCapabilityACSWV03R000 for Application Control Engine (ACE).
Initial version of this MIB module.
